      "content": "but that's the thing... it doesn't feel like a \"small shift\" is gonna fix this. i've tried all the little changes. the therapy, the habits, the new jobs. it's like the universe just resets me every single time. it feels less like a cycle i can change and more like a trap. like the loop is the only thing that's actually real.",
